description:
Rainbow Dash and Pinkie Pie go on a trip to Manehattan to spend Hearth's Warming day with Soarin and his coltfriend Braeburn but Pinkie becomes progressively more and more pissed as things don't go her way like she feels she is deserved 100% of the time because she has mental problems.
https://x.com/TheTamers12345
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345

The insert song "Learn to Love You More" by Thrack can be found here, go check out their other great stuff!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=06-18IRPWdI

Special thanks to @spookyspookitty on twitter for providing some of the necessary backgrounds.
https://x.com/spookyspookitty
